name: Plain Jane
description: This profiles uses a blend of guaranteed CDs and bonds to earn safe gains that you can count on.

name: Looking Towards Retirement
description: This profile blends bonds with domestic stocks to produce low risk, moderate gains. Consistency is key.

name: Domestic Day Trader
description: Did you ever see 'The Big Short'? Same concept here. Looks to pump and dump positions in domestic markets at every possible chance.

name: International Stock Wizard
description: Are you excited about Elbonia's new entry into financial markets? If so, you'll love this investment profile that looks to buy up stock in countries that do not have traditional financial safeguards in place. As Ben Franklin said, 'No pain, no gain'.

name: Crypto Blitz
description: This profile looks to capitalize on the insanity that is the cryptocurrency market. You'll buy into obscure altcoins as they hit the market and watch them go 'to the moon'!
